tradingMarket.title: Trading Market
tradingMarket.rule-one: 1.NFTs can be purchased with $BBT or Any other Choice of Coins as per users listing criteria.
tradingMarket.rule-two: 2.After NFT is listed in the trading market, operations such as transfer, auction, and staking are not allowed.
tradingMarket.rule-three: 3.The market will charge 15% of the seller's revenue as a service fee, of which 5% is sent to the original Minter. 5% will transfer to the Reward to all NFT holders, and 5% to the Marketing Wallet.
